steps.name: Create new Organization folder with valid random name and return to dashboard
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: A0tl7QVe8bhy9YI
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Click Organization Folder name - 'A0tl7QVe8bhy9YI' on dashboard
Click on the 'Configure the project' link on the Organization Folder status page
